message.body: Hey! Nathaniel in Philly here, how are you?
Philly, huh? This is jason, currently stuck in a traffic jam on i95 in jersey! Headed to DC. What do you get into in Philly?
Hey Jason. I just returned home from a bike ride, then am going to do a little painting job. Hope you're going some place fun!
Hi again, just arrived in DC, visiting another friend. how did your painting job go? do you like philly?
I like Philly. Too humid in the summer... But I'm getting to the beach w/ my gf this wkend. Now i'm just kicking it on the stoop w/ a Becks 4 pack
Oh yeah, what beach are you going to? Doing anything to honor your country this wknd?
Rehoboth in Delaware. Not much to honor in my opinion. You?
Not much to honor?!? Well just remember this wknd while youre relaxing on the beach that people died so you could do that. i'm reminded of a bumper sticker i
saw recently: 'before you burn the flag, be sure to wrap yourself in it'!
